{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "寻狗_枯井街坊",
  "entry": "root",
  "meta": {
    "title": "寻狗Demo·枯井活计（街坊上门）"
  },
  "nodes": {
    "root": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "narrative": "scenario_枯井",
              "state": "fled",
              "reached": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "done_1"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "n1"
    },
    "done_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "井那边……真的不叫了？哎，不叫了就好，不叫了就好……（他没敢问细节）",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "n1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "小师傅！总算寻到你了。土地庙后头那口枯井，掉了条狗下去——叫了两天两夜咯！",
      "next": "n2"
    },
    "n2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "（压低声）白天听，是狗叫。夜黑头听……像娃儿哭。庙那边没得哪个敢过去。你帮忙捞上来，街坊些凑了钱的。",
      "next": "c1"
    },
    "c1": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "qu",
          "text": "「不就一条狗嘛。带路。」",
          "next": "c_qu"
        },
        {
          "id": "qian",
          "text": "「钱，先拿出来。」",
          "next": "c_qian"
        }
      ]
    },
    "c_qu": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "哎！哎！钱在这点，你先拿到——庙后头，你自己过去要得不？我、我就不陪你过去了哈……",
      "next": "n_pay"
    },
    "c_qian": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "在这点在这点！十五文，一文都不少！……庙后头你自己过去要得不？我实在是、是脚杆不方便……",
      "next": "n_pay"
    },
    "n_pay": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_枯井街坊",
            "signal": "kujing_hired"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n3"
    },
    "n3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（脚杆不方便。刚才一路小跑过来的嘛。）……要得，老子去。",
      "next": "n_go"
    },
    "n_go": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "switchScene",
          "params": {
            "targetScene": "枯井土地庙",
            "targetSpawnPoint": "entry"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    }
  }
